{"title":"在线升级服务器搭建","slug":"在线升级服务器搭建","date":"2023-04-08","updated":"2023-04-08","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/1000.json","excerpt":"<ul><li>top</li><li> 配置 </li><li> 需要文件 </li></ul>","cover":"/gallery/md/1000/1.png","covers":["/gallery/md/1000/1.png","/gallery/md/1000/2.png","/gallery/md/1000/3.png","/gallery/md/1000/4.png","/gallery/md/1000/5.png","/gallery/md/1000/6.png"],"content":"<ul>\n<li>top</li>\n<li>配置</li>\n<li>需要文件</li>\n</ul>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>#top<br>\n网络 top 如图所示：<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/1.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p># 具体配置：<br>\n1. 配置上行路由器 LAN 口地址为：47.242.66.1/24<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/2.png\" alt=\"2\"><br>\n2. 配置 PC2 网口地址为：47.242.66.129，子网掩码为 255.255.255.0，网关为 47.242.66.1<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/3.png\" alt=\"3\"><br>\n3. 关闭 PC2 网络防火墙<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/4.png\" alt=\"4\"><br>\n4.PC2 运行 IPOP(文档下方取)，在 IPOP 中开启 WEB 服务器，在电脑桌面选择创建一个文件夹，web 服务器的根路径选择这个文件夹，点击 start 开启服务器<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/5.png\" alt=\"5\"><br>\n5.PC2 中将 hnk-ax1806 压缩文件 (见文档下方) 解压到 4 步骤中的根目录中<br>\n<img src=\"/gallery/md/1000/6.png\" alt=\"6\"><br>\n6. 手机连接 1806 WIFI，输入密码登录 APP 便可以开始在线升级。</p>\n<p># 需要文件：<br>\n版本升级包、<a href=\"https://xiazai.zol.com.cn/detail/50/490912.shtml\" rel=\"external nofollow noreferrer\">IPOP.exe</a></p>\n","url":"/posts/1000/","min2read":"1","word4post":192,"prev_post":null,"next_post":{"title":"路由器 TC 打流操作","url":"/posts/2100/"},"toc":"","categories":[{"name":"服务器搭建","path":"api/categories/服务器搭建.json","url":"/categories/服务器搭建/"}],"tags":[{"name":"服务器","path":"api/tags/服务器.json","url":"/tags/服务器/"},{"name":"局域网环境","path":"api/tags/局域网环境.json","url":"/tags/局域网环境/"},{"name":"版本升级","path":"api/tags/版本升级.json","url":"/tags/版本升级/"}]}